e-festival-lineups-following-homophobic-comments-3010132">在 2021 年的</a>一次音乐节上发表仇视同性恋的言论后，遭到强烈反对。外貌。</p><p>从那时起，韦斯特分享了大量反犹太言论，首先<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-backlash-3325627">是他在 2022 年 10 月发推文称自己将参加“犹太人的死亡骗局 3 [原文如此]”。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-suspended-from-clubhouse-over-anti-semitism-3365462">此后，这位说唱歌手的社交媒体帐户被暂停</a>由于他的言论多次。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-wests-anti-semitic-posts-backlash-3325627">娱乐界的许多人物也谴责了韦斯特</a>，一些代表犹太社区的政治人物和组织也是如此。</p><p>此外，这位明星失去了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/balenciaga-cuts-ties-with-kanye-west-over-antisemitic-comments-3333697">巴黎世家 (Balenciaga</a> )、阿迪达斯 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adidas-ends-kanye-west-deal-in-light-of-rappers-anti-semitic-comments-3335494">Adidas</a> ) 和盖普 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-ends-fashion-partnership-with-gap-3311390">Gap)</a>的品牌合作，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kanye-west-has-honorary-doctorate-degree-rescinded-over-disgusting-and-condemnable-statements-3363824">撤销了芝加哥艺术学院的荣誉学位</a>。阿迪达斯后来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/adidas-to-donate-kanye-west-yeezy-profits-to-charity-fighting-antisemitism-3446052">将韦斯特剩余的 Yeezy 鞋库存的收益捐赠给了反犹太主义组织</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scott-brings-out-kanye-west-during-rome-live-stream-3479523">Travis Scott 在罗马直播期间提及 Kanye West 的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
